<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca1a1192-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s971d"><num value="971d">§ 971d.</num><heading> Effect on valid existing Alaskan rights</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in sections 971a to 971e of this title shall affect adversely any valid existing rights.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idca1a1193-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-01/ch848/s4">Aug. 1, 1956, ch. 848, § 4</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70/898">70 Stat. 898</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
